OL,3,CPopular Christmas market cancelled
OL,4,Cbecause of 'escalating costs'
OL,6,FOne of the South West's major
OL,7,FChristmas Markets has announced it has
OL,8,Fbeen cancelled.
OL,10,FPadstow Christmas Food Market has
OL,11,Fhosted world famous chefs for 17 years.
OL,13,FBut organisers have emailed traders to
OL,14,Fsay it won't be happening this year
OL,15,Fbecause of "unforeseen circumstances".
OL,17,FSome businesses are saying they have
OL,18,Flost thousands of pounds in deposits.
