OL,3,CPopular Christmas market cancelled
OL,4,Cbecause of 'escalating costs'
OL,6,FGeorge Mald, from Cornish Rock Gin,
OL,7,Fsaid: "#4,000 is basically what the
OL,8,Fbill is. I've had no communication, no
OL,9,Femails, and I've chased them Friday,
OL,10,FSaturday, Sunday.
OL,12,F"I've had no reply. From what I've
OL,13,Fgathered from 10 other traders -
OL,14,Fthey've received an email saying
OL,15,Fthere's no deposit refund."
OL,17,FNaomi Cartwright, from Padstow Candle
OL,18,FCompany, said: "It's much a massive
OL,19,Fincome for such a small four-day
OL,20,Fevent. It's the majority of my yearly
OL,21,Fincome, because I'm very small."
