OL,3,CPopular Christmas market cancelled
OL,4,Cbecause of 'escalating costs'
OL,6,FErol Sadik, from Post House Interiors
OL,7,FLynmouth, said: "I will say disaster,
OL,8,FI know that's a strong word but I will
OL,9,Fsay disaster and it could put some
OL,10,Fpeople into a very dark place.
OL,12,F"We want to know what's happened to
OL,13,Four deposit money, and we want justice
OL,14,Ffor all the traders involved."
OL,16,FIn response, the event organiser Tina
OL,17,FEvans said: "It is with great sadness
OL,18,Fand regret that I have been left with
OL,19,Fno alternative but to cancel the 2024
OL,20,FPadstow Christmas Festival.
