OL,6,F"With escalating costs and lack of
OL,7,Fsponsorship the event has become
OL,8,Ffinancially non viable.
OL,10,F"Having paid out deposits and initial
OL,11,Fcosts it has become painfully obvious
OL,12,Fthat the festival could not carry on.
OL,14,F"So to minimise the financial loss as
OL,15,Ffar as possible to cancel now is the
OL,16,Fbest option."
